---
title: Loaded Turkey Melt Bar One recipe—endless ways to enjoy!
description: How do you make everyone happy at dinnertime? A DIY grilled turkey and cheese sandwich bar! Keep it simple with melty mild cheddar, turkey, and mayo or get tangy with honey mustard, tomato, and lettuce on crusty sourdough. If you ordered extras, add sliced apple and Swiss to the mix. With crispy roasted potato wedges on the side, everyone at the table will say “cheese!”

